      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This high-revving power unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The suspension maintains excellent damping characteristics and the steering rack remains tight and communicative. While the exterior shows minor road rash consistent with its age, the powertrain and drivetrain remain in excellent form for the performance-oriented driver.",
